{"word":"παῦρος","slug":"παῦρος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>παῦρος</b></el> <el>(παῦρος, ον,) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:παύω'><el>παύω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>little, small</i>, of Time, <i>short</i>, <b><a href='S:Hesiod'>Hes.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Pindar'>Pind.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b>of number, <i>few</i>, <b><a href='S:Homer'>Hom.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Hesiod'>Hes.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a>: <a href='S:Comparative'>comp.</a> <el>παυρότερος</el>, <i>fewer</i>, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b>;—<a href='S:neuter'>neut.</a> <a href='S:plural'>pl.</a> <el>παῦρα</el> as <a href='S:Adverb'>adv.</a> <i>few times, seldom</i>, <b><a href='S:Hesiod'>Hes.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}